# Content Automation Pipeline — Implementation Plan

A fully autonomous daily pipeline that discovers trending tech topics from Reddit and RSS feeds, generates 1 short-form video + 3 text-with-image posts using AI, publishes to X/LinkedIn/YouTube, and notifies via Telegram + email — all monitored through a live dashboard.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys Required**: You will need to create accounts and get API keys for:
> - Reddit (PRAW app credentials) — free
> - X/Twitter Developer API — free tier has read-only; **Basic tier ($100/mo)** needed for write access
> - LinkedIn Developer App — free (OAuth 2.0 approval process)
> - YouTube Data API v3 — free via Google Cloud Console
> - Pexels API — free
> - Google Gemini API — you already have this
> - Telegram Bot Token (via @BotFather) — free

> [!WARNING]
> **X/Twitter API Write Access**: The free tier v2 API only allows read. Posting requires the **Basic** tier ($100/month) or finding an alternative service. We can start with the other platforms and add X later if needed.

## Pipeline Data Flow

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["⏰ Daily Trigger<br/>Windows Task Scheduler"] --> B["📡 Source Fetcher"]
    B --> B1["Reddit PRAW<br/>r/artificial, r/MachineLearning..."]
    B --> B2["RSS Feeds<br/>TechCrunch, HN, Verge..."]
    B1 --> C["🧠 Topic Ranker<br/>Gemini API — pick top 4"]
    B2 --> C
    C --> D1["✍️ Text Generator<br/>3 posts w/ Gemini"]
    C --> D2["🎬 Video Generator<br/>1 short w/ script"]
    D1 --> E1["🖼️ Image Fetcher<br/>Pexels API"]
    D2 --> F1["🗣️ TTS Narration<br/>edge-tts"]
    D2 --> F2["🎥 Stock Footage<br/>Pexels Video API"]
    F1 --> G["🎞️ Video Composer<br/>MoviePy + Captions"]
    F2 --> G
    E1 --> H["📤 Publishers"]
    G --> H
    H --> H1["𝕏 Twitter"]
    H --> H2["💼 LinkedIn"]
    H --> H3["▶️ YouTube Shorts"]
    H --> I["📊 Dashboard DB<br/>SQLite"]
    I --> J["🖥️ Web Dashboard<br/>FastAPI + Modern UI"]
    H --> K["🔔 Notifications"]
    K --> K1["📱 Telegram"]
    K --> K2["📧 Email"]
```

## Daily Output

| Content | Platforms | Details |
|---|---|---|
| **1 Video** (30–60s) | YouTube Shorts + X + LinkedIn | Pexels footage + TTS narration + burned captions, 9:16 vertical |
| **3 Text Posts** | X + LinkedIn | AI-written casual+educational posts with Pexels images |

