### Orchestrator (Phase 7)

#### [NEW] [pipeline/orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/content_automation_pipeline/pipeline/orchestrator.py)
Main pipeline entry point:
1. Notify "Pipeline started" via Telegram
2. Fetch trending topics (Reddit + RSS)
3. Select top 4 topics via AI
4. Generate 3 text posts + 1 video
5. Fetch images for text posts
6. Publish all content to platforms
7. Log results to SQLite
8. Notify completion via Telegram + email
9. Handle errors with retry + error notifications

#### [NEW] [run_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/content_automation_pipeline/run_pipeline.py)
CLI entry point — `python run_pipeline.py` triggers one full run.
Flags: `--dry-run` (generate without posting), `--dashboard` (start dashboard server)

